data.description: Expanded Trenton Model.  3 Bedrooms 2 baths. Newer roof. Freshly painted and New Carpet. Large fenced Yard. Laminate flooring thru-out 1st floor. Spacious kitchen w/bay window, huge pantry, all appliances included. Dining area with ceiling fan and sliders to patio and fenced Yard. Large master with walk-in closet with organizers. Finished basement and workshop. Ample storage. 2 car garage. Large Shed. Expanded Drive way area for boat and extra parking. This property is not located in a flood zone map amendment under additional info.
